        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group quote-modified\" data-post=\"5\" data-topic=\"171724\">\n<blockquote>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"171724\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>I\u2019ve never seen that.  What\u2019s the Champagne?</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Selosse, and by the looks of it not a young bottle!  Let us know how it shows!</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Correct.  I bought it from Acker, and the lot description made no mention of this (and described the badly scuffed and soiled label as lightly so).  I\u2019ve now been emailing them for a month about how they want to address it.</p>",
